title: Deja Vu (1985) Shelley Winters Claire Bloom et al
description:
This is NOT to be confused with several movies having the same title. it is a romantic fantasy involving ballet and "coming back" from the beyond. People who liked Black Swan should enjoy this,although it is nowhere near the same level.

The ageing Shelley Winters and Claire Bloom are a nice touch, though the romantic leads are Jaclyn Smith and Nigel Terry.

I usually have a good response when I post romantic nostalgia - "The sentimental ones are issued sparingly, so they're always in demand"... see if you can identify that quote!

Ripped from tape; in mpg format.
